many per year A financial product, called real estate trust investment funds. When it goes public, Internet companies can also be divided into 30%, which is a Profitable way. \"<br/> second aspect, Wanda has a huge advantage, the flow of people is very great. Wang Jianlin said that there were 1.6 billion people in Wanda last year and it is expected to exceed 2 billion this year. \"In 2020, according to the most conservative estimates, there will be more than 6 billion people, and we will enter Wanda Plaza, hotels, resorts, and the most conservative estimate. According to one person once a month, active users, at least 500 million active Users. There may be more in the future. These resources are the customers who will issue Internet financial loans in the future. Because of his consumption data, in the first and second tier cities, if it is in Beijing and Shanghai, it may not be recorded completely, but for the third line, In the fourth-tier cities, the consumption data is very complete.” Wang Jianlin exemplified that “there are less than 400,000 people in Langfang, and the removal of children and elderly people who do not have the ability to consume may be 300,000 people, which means one. People spend less than a week on average, and go to it once every four to five days. He buys things, watches movies, eats, sings, etc., and it will become the data we have. According to this complete data chain, we can judge the spending power of this person. \"And his consumption preferences.\"<br/> \"There are more Wanda Plazas now. We are opening 20 this year because we will open 50 Wanda Plazas. After three or five years, everyone will find that we will open 80 to 100 a year. With such a large number of openings, there are four to five hundred merchants in each square. The collection period is our investment, and we have the collection period. In 2020, we will have about 400,000 POS machines. These merchants are also the target of our credit card loan. Because we have the POS machine, our loan, we don’t need to open the store offline. Second, we are absolutely \"Safety.\"<br/> \"Why is it absolutely safe? We are designing a cloud POS, which will be replaced in the third quarter. There will be two or three billion merchants, replace it, and replace it with the model we designed. Will lend 1 million, repay each day, how much is designed every day, cloud POS will move our share and interest. The rest does not affect which bank you have cooperation with, very safe, the financial mode of the Internet This is very simple.\"<br/> Wang Jianlin said that at present, Wanda\'s O2O is going in these two directions. One is to spend money to increase the sense of experience and increase the viscosity. Second, through Internet finance, gain profits and increase the further expansion and development of O2O. Ma Yun asked: \"How much does it cost to do O2O?\" Ma said: \"Transformation is like pulling a tooth. You have to stop working. You have to suffer. You have to pay time and money. The price is a must. Your business transformation must pay a huge price. I don\'t know how much you are going to pay and what kind of cost to realize your Wanda\'s transformation. Because I hear you making money, What are you not making money? How are you prepared?” Wang Jianlin said that transformation must pay a price. Wanda’s 27 years of development and history have always changed. At the same time, he also answered the data cooperation and the ecological circle, but Ma Yun is not satisfied with this: \"I still don\'t understand how much Wanda wants to pay, I only understand how many people you are looking for to bear the cost. \"\"<br/> \"The cost is too great, I am poor, what is the transformation?\" Wang Jianlin believes that no company will transform for transformation, the purpose is to make the company better, and more Sustainable. Finally, Wang Jianlin said bluntly: \"I didn\'t plan to pay too much!\" <br/> At the same time, Wang Jianlin did not forget to ridicule